  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2681530/extras/b6e3b78a60fb3311ecd2ae1b3e51a30a.poster.avif?t=1765514339\" width=608 height=88 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2681530/extras/b6e3b78a60fb3311ecd2ae1b3e51a30a.webm?t=1765514339\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2681530/extras/b6e3b78a60fb3311ecd2ae1b3e51a30a.mp4?t=1765514339\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Explore endless roads. Engage in heart-pounding drifts through cityscapes, mountain passes, and more!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2681530/extras/aa388b8f1510d6a2032a4e8e1c183267.avif?t=1765514339\" width=608 height=88 /></span><br>Teamwork makes the dream work! Join forces with your friends in coop game play. Coordinate your moves, execute synchronized drifts<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2681530/extras/18ea9b75554a9d2e889961a124389dd2.avif?t=1765514339\" width=608 height=88 /></span><br>Choose from a fleet of high-performance vehicles and personalize them to match your style.<br><br>Whether you're a seasoned drift pro or a newcomer to the genre, our intuitive controls ensure a smooth and enjoyable gaming experience for players of all skill levels.<br><br>Are you ready to embark on the drift adventure of a lifetime? Gather your crew, rev up your engines, and become the Drift Masters",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2681530/extras/b6e3b78a60fb3311ecd2ae1b3e51a30a.poster.avif?t=1765514339\" width=608 height=88 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2681530/extras/b6e3b78a60fb3311ecd2ae1b3e51a30a.webm?t=1765514339\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2681530/extras/b6e3b78a60fb3311ecd2ae1b3e51a30a.mp4?t=1765514339\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Explore endless roads. Engage in heart-pounding drifts through cityscapes, mountain passes, and more!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2681530/extras/aa388b8f1510d6a2032a4e8e1c183267.avif?t=1765514339\" width=608 height=88 /></span><br>Teamwork makes the dream work! Join forces with your friends in coop game play. Coordinate your moves, execute synchronized drifts<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2681530/extras/18ea9b75554a9d2e889961a124389dd2.avif?t=1765514339\" width=608 height=88 /></span><br>Choose from a fleet of high-performance vehicles and personalize them to match your style.<br><br>Whether you're a seasoned drift pro or a newcomer to the genre, our intuitive controls ensure a smooth and enjoyable gaming experience for players of all skill levels.<br><br>Are you ready to embark on the drift adventure of a lifetime? Gather your crew, rev up your engines, and become the Drift Masters",
